dct_description_sm: drawn and reproduced by Survey Department, Lagos, Nigeria.
Shows boundaries, headquarters, principal and minor towns and villages, roads and railways.
Includes key to native courts in the Bornu, Adamawa, Benue, and eastern provinces.
